#. Tag: title
#: patterns.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating patterns"
msgstr "Kreiranje vzorcev"

#. Tag: title
#: patterns.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting &kxstitch;"
msgstr "Zagon &kxstitch;"

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:6
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When starting &kxstitch; you will be presented with a blank canvas of the "
"default size. This is also the case when selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. The default sizes can be set in the pattern properties dialog "
"by enabling the set as default checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Ko zaženete &kxstitch; vam bo prikazano prazno platno privzete velikosti. To "
"velja tudi, ko izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Privzete velikosti "
"lahko nastavite v pogovornem oknu lastnosti vzorca, tako da omogočite "
"potrditveno polje Nastavi kot privzeto."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the default size is not suitable for your planned pattern, you can use "
"the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>File Properties</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog to change it. Adjust the values as required "
"and after clicking on <guibutton>OK</guibutton>, the pattern will be resized "
"to suit."
msgstr ""
"Če privzeta velikost ni primerna za vaš načrtovani vzorec, jo lahko "
"spremenite v pogovornem oknu <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Lastnosti datoteke</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Po "
"potrebi prilagodite vrednosti in po kliku na <guibutton>V redu</guibutton> "
"bo velikost vzorca prilagojena."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Before creating a pattern you will need to add some flosses to the palette "
"using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Palette</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Palette "
"Manager</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This will enable the tools in the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu></menuchoice> menu and toolbar. See the "
"<link linkend=\"PaletteManagerDialog\">Palette Manager Dialog</link> for "
"further information."
msgstr ""
"Preden ustvarite vzorec, boste morali paleti dodati nekaj nitk z uporabo "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Palette</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Upravljalnika palet</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. To bo omogočilo orodja v meniju in orodni vrstici "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu></menuchoice>. Za dodatne informacije "
"si oglejte <link linkend=\"PaletteManagerDialog\">pogovorno okno "
"upravljalnika palet</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: patterns.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "Importing Images"
msgstr "Uvažanje slik"

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kxstitch; allows you to import an image. A dialog will be displayed that "
"previews the image based on the default import options."
msgstr ""
"&kxstitch; omogoča uvoz slik. Prikaže se pogovorno okno s predogledom slike "
"na podlagi privzetih možnosti uvoza."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The initial size of the pattern will be based on the default pattern size."
msgstr "Začetna velikost vzorca bo temeljila na privzeti velikosti vzorca."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Options for importing allow you to change the floss scheme used and to limit "
"the number of colors. You can also change the scaling to reduce or enlarge "
"the final pattern."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti za uvoz vam omogočajo, da spremenite uporabljeno shemo nitke in "
"omejite število barv. Spremenite lahko tudi velikost, da zmanjšate ali "
"povečate končni vzorec."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking the <guilabel>Use fractionals</guilabel> checkbox will enable the "
"use of fractional stitches to give more detail for any given pattern size."
msgstr ""
"Če označite potrditveno polje <guilabel>Uporabi ulomke</guilabel>, boste "
"omogočili uporabo ulomkov za več podrobnosti za katero koli velikost vzorca."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking the <guilabel>Ignore color</guilabel> checkbox will allow the "
"selection of a color within the image which will then be considered as the "
"transparent color and ignored during the import."
msgstr ""
"Če označite potrditveno polje <guilabel>Prezri barvo</guilabel>, boste "
"omogočili izbiro barve znotraj slike, ki bo nato obravnavana kot prosojna "
"barva in med uvozom prezrta."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After the image has been imported, an additional dock window will be "
"available giving a preview of the original image without any color "
"transitions."
msgstr ""
"Ko je slika uvožena, bo na voljo dodatno priklopno okno s predogledom "
"izvirne slike brez barvnih prehodov."

#. Tag: title
#: patterns.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Background Images"
msgstr "Slike ozadja"

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can insert an image as a background to the editor window. This is useful "
"if importing the image is not desirable or gives poor results."
msgstr ""
"V okno urejevalnika lahko vstavite sliko kot ozadje. To je uporabno, če uvoz "
"slike ni zaželen ali daje slabe rezultate."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The image is normally scaled to cover the entire pattern grid. This may not "
"be suitable, therefore you can use the select tool to select an area that "
"you want to cover and then select the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Fit Background Image to Selection</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. "
"This will rescale the image to fit within the selected area. You can "
"continue doing this until you are happy with the result, even after you have "
"started adding stitches."
msgstr ""
"Slika je običajno prilagojena tako, da pokriva celotno mrežo vzorca. To "
"morda ni primerno, zato lahko uporabite orodje za izbiro, da izberete "
"območje, ki ga želite pokriti, in nato izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilagodi sliko ozadja izboru</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. To bo spremenilo velikost slike, da se prilega izbranemu "
"območju. To lahko nadaljujete, dokler ne boste zadovoljni z rezultatom, tudi "
"potem, ko ste že začeli dodajati šive."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is no limit to the number of background images that can be added. "
"Although practical limits of the menus will determine how many can be added. "
"The background images are stored within the document, so they will be "
"available when the pattern is reloaded."
msgstr ""
"Število slik za ozadje, ki jih je mogoče dodati, ni omejeno. Čeprav bodo "
"praktične omejitve menijev določile, koliko jih je mogoče dodati. Slike "
"ozadja so shranjene v dokumentu, tako da bodo na voljo, ko bo vzorec znova "
"naložen."

#. Tag: title
#: patterns.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pattern Libraries"
msgstr "Knjižnice vzorcev"

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The pattern library manager can be used to store patterns for insertion into "
"the working pattern. They can be categorized into a hierarchy of categories "
"and subcategories with multiple root nodes in the library list. The Alphabet "
"tool makes use of these libraries to provide an alphabet of insertable "
"characters that can be assigned an associated key."
msgstr ""
"Upravljalnik knjižnice vzorcev se lahko uporablja za shranjevanje vzorcev za "
"vstavljanje v delovni vzorec. Lahko jih kategoriziramo v hierarhijo "
"kategorij in podkategorij z več korenskimi vozlišči na seznamu knjižnic. "
"Orodje Alphabet uporablja te knjižnice za zagotavljanje abecede znakov, ki "
"jih je mogoče vstaviti, ki jim je mogoče dodeliti pripadajočo tipko."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The library manager is a non modal dialog and can be left open whilst "
"working on your pattern. You can select different libraries as needed and "
"then drag and drop library patterns onto the working pattern."
msgstr ""
"Upravljalnik knjižnice je nemodalno pogovorno okno in ga lahko pustite "
"odprtega, medtem ko delate na svojem vzorcu. Po potrebi lahko izberete "
"različne knjižnice in nato povlečete in spustite vzorce knjižnic na delovni "
"vzorec."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adding new category headings can be done with a &RMB; on either an existing "
"entry, to create a sub category, or on a blank space on the library list, to "
"create a new root entry, and selecting the <guimenuitem>New Category</"
"guimenuitem> option. Enter the name of the category and click <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Dodajanje novih naslovov kategorij lahko storite z &RMB; na obstoječem "
"vnosu, da ustvarite podkategorijo, ali na praznem prostoru na seznamu "
"knjižnic, da ustvarite nov korenski vnos, in izberete možnost "
"<guimenuitem>Nova kategorija</guimenuitem>. Vnesite ime kategorije in "
"kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creating a new library pattern is done by selecting an area of your working "
"pattern, copying and pasting to one of the existing categories."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite nov vzorec knjižnice tako, da izberete območje vašega delovnega "
"vzorca, kopirate in prilepite v eno od obstoječih kategorij."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each library pattern has properties, accessed by its context menu. These "
"properties include size, floss scheme, baseline value and associated key. "
"The baseline value is used by the Alphabet tool to adjust the height of a "
"character above, negative values, or below the insertion point. The "
"associated key is again used by the Alphabet tool to match with the key "
"pressed on the keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Vsak vzorec knjižnice ima lastnosti, do katerih dostopate prek kontekstnega "
"menija. Te lastnosti vključujejo velikost, shemo nitke, osnovno vrednost in "
"pripadajoči ključ. Osnovno vrednost uporablja orodje Alphabet za "
"prilagoditev višine znaka nad, negativne vrednosti ali pod točko "
"vstavljanja. Povezano tipko spet uporabi orodje Alphabet, da se ujema s "
"tipko, pritisnjeno na tipkovnici."
